---
// SupportBanner.astro - Banner clickable completo
---
<aside class="support-banner">
  <a href="https://ko-fi.com/emtsyslab" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="support-link">
    <span class="coffee-emoji">☕</span>
    <span class="support-text">¿Te resultó útil este contenido? <strong>Invítame a un café</strong></span>
  </a>
</aside>

<style>
  .support-banner {
    background: rgba(137, 180, 250, 0.08);
    border-left: 3px solid rgba(137, 180, 250, 0.5);
    margin: 2rem 0;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }
  
  .support-banner:hover {
    background: rgba(137, 180, 250, 0.12);
    border-left-color: rgba(137, 180, 250, 0.7);
  }
  
  .support-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  
  .coffee-emoji {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .support-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .support-text strong {
    color: #89b4fa;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  
  .support-banner:hover .support-text strong {
    border-bottom-color: #89b4fa;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .support-link {
      padding: 0.875rem 1rem;
    }
    
    .coffee-emoji {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
    
    .support-text {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
  }
</style>
